---
// Component Imports
import Page from "../layouts/Page.astro";
import Head from "../layouts/Head.astro";
import Hero from "../layouts/WorkHero.astro";
import mangesh from "../images/mangesh.png";
import mangeshFull from "../images/mangesh-lg.png";
import Modal from "../components/Modal.astro";
import ButtonIcon from "../components/ButtonIcon.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
import { Image, Picture } from "@astrojs/image/components";

const meta = {
  title: "Mangesh Thombare",
  description: "Portfolio website for a game designer.",
};
---

<Page>
  <Head slot="head" {meta} />
  <Hero />
  <main
    id="content-wrapper"
    class="container mx-auto px-8 py-6 dark:bg-dark-900 dark:text-white md:px-0 md:py-24"
  >
    <div
      class="container my-2 min-h-full space-y-5 px-4 text-left leading-relaxed lg:px-8"
    >
      <div id="pagination" class="flex flex-wrap items-center space-x-4">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="hover:ease hover:text-geraldine-500 hover:transition-all hover:duration-200 focus:border-b-4 focus:border-slate-500 focus:outline-none"
          tabindex="0">Home</a
        >
        <Icon name="icon-arrow" class="w-4 h-4" />
        <a
          href="/work/#content-wrapper"
          class="hover:ease hover:text-geraldine-500 hover:transition-all hover:duration-200 focus:border-b-4 focus:border-slate-500 focus:outline-none"
          tabindex="0">Work</a
        >
        <Icon name="icon-arrow" class="w-4 h-4" />
        <a
          href="#"
          class="focus:border-b-4 focus:border-slate-500 focus:outline-none"
          tabindex="0">Mangesh Thombare</a
        >
      </div>

      <div class="text-f-xl my-6 font-display font-semibold">
        Mangesh
        <span class="text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-300">Thombare</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start md:flex-row">
        <div
          class="mx-2 my-4 flex flex-shrink-0 border-2 border-gray-200 shadow-lg hover:border-geraldine-400 dark:border-gray-800 dark:hover:border-geraldine-400 md:w-1/2 lg:w-auto"
        >
          <Image
            class="object-contain w-full h-auto dark:filter dark:brightness-75 dark:contrast-125"
            src={mangesh}
            alt="Mangesh Thombare"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8 flex flex-col space-y-3 px-2 md:pl-6">
          <p>
            This was a portfolio website project for a game designer. His
            requirements were a responsive website which showcased his CV,
            embedded videos and documents of his completed projects and lastly a
            contact form.
          </p>

          <ul class="list-inside list-decimal">
            <li>Portfolio website.</li>
            <li>Responsive design.</li>
            <li>Embedded videos and documents.</li>
            <li>Modal for images.</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div>
              <ButtonIcon
                id="modal3-trigger"
                color="bg-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-600 dark:bg-emerald-400 dark:hover:bg-emerald-500 cursor-pointer py-3"
                iconName="icon-picture"
                iconClass="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-current">Screenshot</ButtonIcon
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex py-10">
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <svg
            class="inline-block h-5 w-5 fill-current text-geraldine-600 md:h-10 md:w-10"
            aria-label="Quotes"
            viewBox="0 0 512 512"
          >
            <path
              d="M464 256h-80v-64c0-35.3 28.7-64 64-64h8c13.3 0 24-10.7 24-24V56c0-13.3-10.7-24-24-24h-8c-88.4 0-160 71.6-160 160v240c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h128c26.5 0 48-21.5 48-48V304c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48zm-288 0H96v-64c0-35.3 28.7-64 64-64h8c13.3 0 24-10.7 24-24V56c0-13.3-10.7-24-24-24h-8C71.6 32 0 103.6 0 192v240c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h128c26.5 0 48-21.5 48-48V304c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3 px-4 md:px-8">
          <p>
            Akshay designed my portfolio website. The best part about working
            with him was that, I got a site fully customized and tailored to my
            needs. It is easy to navigate and works seamlessly on all platforms
            mobiles, tablets or PCs. When certain changes had to be made, they
            were delivered with precision within 24 hours of request. He has the
            patience to work at your pace every step of the way. You can have a
            fully personalized experience at an affordable price. It has been a
            pleasure working with Akshay.
          </p>

          <p class="text-right font-semibold">- Mangesh Thombare</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-end">
          <svg
            class="inline-block h-5 w-5 fill-current text-geraldine-600 md:h-10 md:w-10"
            aria-label="Quotes"
            viewBox="0 0 512 512"
          >
            <path
              d="M464 32H336c-26.5 0-48 21.5-48 48v128c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h80v64c0 35.3-28.7 64-64 64h-8c-13.3 0-24 10.7-24 24v48c0 13.3 10.7 24 24 24h8c88.4 0 160-71.6 160-160V80c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48zm-288 0H48C21.5 32 0 53.5 0 80v128c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h80v64c0 35.3-28.7 64-64 64h-8c-13.3 0-24 10.7-24 24v48c0 13.3 10.7 24 24 24h8c88.4 0 160-71.6 160-160V80c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Modal triggerId="modal3-trigger" title="Mangesh Thombare">
    <div class="mt-3 grid place-content-center">
      <Picture
        class="dark:filter dark:brightness-75 dark:contrast-125"
        src={mangeshFull}
        alt="Mangesh Thombare Full Image"
        widths={[300, 450, 600]}
        sizes="(max-width: 768px) 300px, (max-width: 1024px) 450px, 600px"
        aspectRatio={1.24}
      />
    </div>
  </Modal>
</Page>
